{"tid":686731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方拘捕22歲女子涉旺角騷亂 被控兩項暴動罪 下周提堂","createTime":"2018-06-01T14:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T03:10:36.000Z","uid":70063,"like":8,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e805ca7587bb91ccd730c07b26e45e80da78745b","tid":686731,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"2016年農曆大年初二凌晨發生的旺角騷亂，警方昨日拘捕22歲女子，案件下周提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方於2016年7月7日在青衣區拘捕一名女子，涉嫌參與暴動，該名女子其後在2017年1月拒保候查。警方經進一步調查及諮詢法律意見後，昨日在青衣區再拘捕該名22歲女子，涉嫌參與暴動，她已被控以兩項暴動罪，案件將於6月6日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方至今共拘捕91人，80名男子及11名女子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1230636/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1230636%2F&d=iwrpB9Jvb375Ye5ZGadx1C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8df8cacd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1230636%2F&h=63bbf926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1230636/</a>"},{"pid":"692afb67d2b4dad45cf04438040d60047a2cc32f","tid":686731,"uid":34103,"like":9,"dislike":23,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e74095da1e614d134dbeb5860378fcfdf343816","tid":686731,"uid":171107,"like":18,"dislike":6,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"692afb67d2b4dad45cf04438040d60047a2cc32f","tid":686731,"uid":34103,"like":9,"dislike":23,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"都養緊你全家啦，唔爭在"},{"pid":"2f328d44da90186e99a96747bbf85f8728bd1940","tid":686731,"uid":34103,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3035b365e1f68eb1b54fcc3276dac15d7f190bc1","tid":686731,"uid":28624,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:28:32.000Z","msg":"都估到呢d post5毛最快留言<br />\n<br />\nJR呢？next<img src=\"/assets/fa